gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從冇咗 scale charge，purely 非訴訟又有肉食嘅好似係 IPO, M&amp;A 等等 commercial 野？嗰啲嘢又唔覺 robot replace 到喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"17d6529da62b41560e17cd9da5872900c628b2cd","tid":100761,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哂氣 香港一定唔會<br />\n科技落後</blockquote><br />\n係香港咁撚落後,機械ai有排都唔淪到香港</blockquote><br />\n你唔跟人用ai就成個香港被人取代<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然無成個咁誇張既"},{"pid":"ca3a71d0ec680d4f167aff98633ad27a14fe4323","tid":100761,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:00:25.000Z","msg":"其實照計越過人工既工種，研究機構係越有傾向放資源去發展ai,唔知邊個高薪工種最唔好彩被人睇上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364f1f3a976bcc8b2976f9c302542f6b10c1c630","tid":100761,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實照計越高人工既工種，研究機構係越有傾向放資源去發展ai,唔知邊個高薪工種最唔好彩先被人睇上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1aabd4aca7ef984de0a7751a6dce751cbd3aebef","tid":100761,"uid":36324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>哂氣 香港一定唔會<br />\n科技落後</blockquote><br />\n係香港咁撚落後,機械ai有排都唔淪到香港</blockquote><br />\n你唔跟人用ai就成個香港被人取代<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然無成個咁誇張既</blockquote><br />\n香港啲都屎忽有呢啲覺誤先算啦"},{"pid":"3227085ee6a075a2b17323195d95dc48c790cc3d","tid":100761,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:04:01.000Z","msg":"麥玲玲 ((高危指數：0.0001%)"},{"pid":"969988cea993df20a6014f882e88819381fbab48","tid":100761,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb38378462c8402c040f26b77aad318449a14223","tid":100761,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:14:53.000Z","msg":"IT狗即將捲土重來"},{"pid":"d59302a26a004a811a1372074b7ecdd180cc981c","tid":100761,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:49:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>IT狗即將捲土重來</blockquote><br />\n其實ux designer都係高危，個人諗為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81f8c9fa98e14c34aa740bbbf1d43b3d8d8ea54","tid":100761,"uid":72203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T03:22:38.000Z","msg":"AUDIT呢D垃圾工種幾時俾人淘汰"}]}